## 📊 Visual Design Spec (Admin Notice Feed Card)

The notice feed card leverages EasyCart's premium tech-modern styling system:

| State | Color/Indicator | Icon | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Member Removal** | Red Border (`--danger`) | 🗑️ | Triggered when an organizer or admin removes a family member. |
| **Member Added** | Green Border (`--success`) | 👤 | Triggered when a new user joins a family plan. |
| **System Info** | Yellow/Slate Border | ℹ️ | Triggered for other operational events. |

> [!TIP]
> The notice feed utilizes a scrollable container with a standard `max-height: 400px` to keep the layout exceptionally clean and mobile-friendly, avoiding page overflow.
